data.description: Nicely updated single level home in the Prescott Country Club. R.V. slab with electric hookup year-round golf with reasonable green fees, in a very nice tight knit community to live in. HOA fee of $57.00 A YEAR, Golf cart garage and workshop. VERY PRIVATE OASIS BACK YARD, FULLY FENCED Gas fireplace, New insulated garage door and opener, new refrigerator, gas cooktop, new microwave with outside vent and LED lighting. Extended bar/island with new granite counter tops and back splash. Real crystal chandelier with dimmable LED lights, overhead can dimmable LED lights above the bar. New front door, new storm doors front and rear, new tile and toilet in master bath. New toilet in 2nd bath New central air, new roof 2016, Water heater and furnace 2015
